<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:18:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台积电第二季度利润增长36% 好于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q2-profit-rises-36-better-than-forecast-2024-07-18/</link><description>台湾芯片制造商台积电周四公布第二季度净利润增长 36%，超出市场预期，因人工智能应用中使用的半导体需求激增。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q2-profit-rises-36-better-than-forecast-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：随着贸易紧张局势加剧，筹码下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-18/</link><description>Ankur Banerjee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中美芯片战加深，亚洲科技股下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asia-tech-stocks-skid-deepening-sino-us-chip-war-2024-07-18/</link><description>亚洲芯片股周四暴跌，因有新闻报道称美国正在考虑对向中国出口先进半导体技术实施更严格的限制，导致华尔街大幅抛售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asia-tech-stocks-skid-deepening-sino-us-chip-war-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普发表评论后，台湾表示致力于加强防御</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-says-committed-strengthening-defence-after-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</link><description>台湾外交部周四表示，台湾致力于加强防御并与美国合作，几天前，共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普被引述称台湾应该为防御付费。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-says-committed-strengthening-defence-after-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪计划在越南积极扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-introduce-three-more-car-models-vietnam-market-2024-07-18/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周四概述了积极扩大其在越南经销网络的计划，本周将在越南开设第一家门店，这对当地竞争对手 VinFast 构成了巨大的挑战。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:30:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-introduce-three-more-car-models-vietnam-market-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>越南向联合国提出南海大陆架延伸主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-files-un-claim-extended-continental-shelf-south-china-sea-2024-07-18/</link><description>越南外交部周四表示，在地区邻国菲律宾采取类似行动一个月后，越南已向联合国提出南海扩展大陆架（ECS）主张。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-files-un-claim-extended-continental-shelf-south-china-sea-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因贸易紧张局势加剧而下跌，日元公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-18/</link><description>由于投资者担心中美贸易紧张局势升级的前景，亚洲股市周四下跌，芯片股领跌，而日元在东京疑似干预后触及六周高点后坚挺。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:02:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>干预幽灵令投资者恐慌，日元飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-spikes-spectre-intervention-spooks-investors-2024-07-18/</link><description>日本日元周四触及六周高点，引发了官方推动行动的猜测，而美元则普遍下跌，因为市场正在为美国几个月后的降息做准备，并等待当天晚些时候在欧洲召开的央行会议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-spikes-spectre-intervention-spooks-investors-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>台积电季度利润大涨36% 超预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-strong-profit-stock-pressured-by-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</link><description>台积电周四公布第二季度净利润增长 36%，超出市场预期，这家台湾芯片制造商乘势而上，推动了人工智能应用中半导体的需求浪潮。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-strong-profit-stock-pressured-by-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>向俄罗斯走私军事技术的男子被判入狱三年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/man-who-smuggled-military-tech-russia-sentenced-3-years-us-jail-2024-07-17/</link><description>美国司法部表示，一名俄罗斯男子周三被判处三年监禁，该男子承认美国指控他向俄罗斯走私大量美国制造的军用级微电子产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/man-who-smuggled-military-tech-russia-sentenced-3-years-us-jail-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：随着科技股下跌、日元飙升，波动性回归</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-17/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:49:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普国家安全顾问呼吁台湾增加国防开支</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-national-security-adviser-calls-taiwan-lift-defense-spending-2024-07-17/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普的一位高级国家安全顾问周三表示，面对中国潜在的侵略，台湾需要大幅增加国防开支。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-national-security-adviser-calls-taiwan-lift-defense-spending-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级代表团强调巴布亚新几内亚的承诺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/high-level-us-delegation-stresses-papua-new-guinea-commitment-2024-07-17/</link><description>美国高级民事和军事代表团本周访问了巴布亚新几内亚，强调美国对中国正在争夺影响力的太平洋战略领土的承诺。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/high-level-us-delegation-stresses-papua-new-guinea-commitment-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示已停止与美国就台湾问题进行军控谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-it-has-halted-arms-control-talks-with-us-over-taiwan-2024-07-17/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中国已停止与美国展开的核军控谈判，以抗议华盛顿向民主治理的台湾岛出售武器，北京声称台湾是其领土。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 18:06:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-it-has-halted-arms-control-talks-with-us-over-taiwan-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>香港记者小组负责人表示，她因新闻自由争议而被《华尔街日报》解雇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-journalist-group-head-says-she-was-fired-by-wsj-amid-press-freedom-row-2024-07-17/</link><description>香港记者协会(HKJA)会长表示，她周三被《华尔街日报》解雇，原因是她拒绝了该报高级编辑提出的与该组织断绝关系、不再倡导媒体自由的要求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-journalist-group-head-says-she-was-fired-by-wsj-amid-press-freedom-row-2024-07-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>